data.description: Welcome to this fantastic single-level home built in 2020, offering spacious living with an open concept design. The primary bedroom is thoughtfully located away from all other rooms for ultimate privacy. With 2,288 square feet of living space, this home provides comfort and room to grow. Enjoy the breathtaking mountain views and Nevada's iconic sunrises and sunsets from the comfort of your new home. This property boasts convenient access to parks, schools, and recreational activities, making it perfect for the outdoor enthusiasts. The 3-car tandem garage provides ample space for your vehicles and storage needs, while RV access parking ensures there's room for all your toys. Inside, you'll find Granite Countertops and Island in the kitchen, adding both style and functionality. Nice Sized Pantry, the washer, dryer, and fridge are included, making this home move-in ready. This home is Priced to Sell! Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours – schedule a viewing today! 1hr Notice required. Sellers are willing to have the carpets professionally cleaned upon COE if the buyer wishes to have it done.  The sellers are contingent upon finding another home out of state, please contact listing agent prior to writing offer. There may be listening devices in the home such as the Ring Doorbell.  BUYER AND BUYER AGENT TO VERIFY ALL! DON'T GET SCAMMED, THIS HOME IS FOR SALE NOT FOR RENT ON FB MARKETPLACE OR CRAIGSLIST.
